---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Indeed Profile Optimization | OPTYP">
  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 px-4 sm:px-8">
    <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#47C6A2]">Home</a> › 
    <a href="/explore" class="hover:text-[#47C6A2]">Explore</a> › 
    <a href="/explore/job-portals" class="hover:text-[#47C6A2]">Job Portals</a> › 
    <span class="text-white">Indeed</span>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="text-center py-12 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">
      Indeed Profile Optimization Service
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">
      Transform your Indeed profile into a recruiter magnet. Professional optimization delivers 
      <strong>45% more job applications</strong> and <strong>3x higher recruiter visibility</strong> within 30 days.
    </p>

    <!-- Hero Image (Responsive & Sharp) -->
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
      <img 
        src="/images/indeed-page2.svg" 
        alt="Indeed Profile Optimization"
        class="w-full max-h-96 object-contain rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-white/10"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 rounded-2xl"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <a href="/#contact" 
       class="glass-btn px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 
              border border-[#47C6A2] text-white shadow-md hover:shadow-[#47C6A2]/50 
              hover:bg-[#47C6A2]/20 hover:scale-105">
      Get Your Indeed Profile Optimized Now
    </a>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain Section -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">The Silent Application Killer You Can’t See</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Your Indeed profile is sabotaging your job search without you knowing it. With over 
      <strong>250 million monthly visitors</strong> and <strong>295 million resumes</strong> in the database, 
      an unoptimized profile simply disappears in the crowd.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here’s the brutal reality: Only <strong>2–5% of job applications</strong> on Indeed get positive responses. 
      Recruiters scan profiles for just <strong>6–8 seconds</strong> before deciding whether to engage.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Hidden Cost -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 my-10 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">The Hidden Cost of Being Invisible</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You’re qualified. You’ve got the right experience. But your applications vanish while less 
      qualified candidates get interview calls.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Every day your profile stays unoptimized costs you opportunities. The average job search 
      drags on <strong>5–6 months</strong> without help. Miss one recruiter call, and you could lose 
      <strong>tens of thousands in potential earnings</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>Your career momentum dies when recruiters can’t find you among 295 million profiles.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">The Solution: Strategic Indeed Profile Optimization</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      <li>Complete Profile Enhancement – 100% profile completion prioritized by Indeed’s algorithm</li>
      <li>Recruiter-Focused Keywords – Get discovered 10x more often with exact search terms</li>
      <li>Professional Summary Optimization – Compel recruiters to stop scrolling</li>
      <li>Skills Section Mastery – Align with Indeed’s Smart Sourcing tech</li>
      <li>Experience Section Transformation – Achievements over duties with measurable results</li>
      <li>Indeed Apply Integration – Generate 45% more application starts</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 my-10 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">What’s In It For You: Measurable Career Acceleration</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="glassmorphism p-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-2">Dramatic Visibility Increases</h3>
        <p>45% more application opportunities, 3x recruiter engagement, 50% faster job search.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glassmorphism p-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-2">Application Success Rates</h3>
        <p>20–25% higher response rates, hidden job opportunities, multiple interview calls.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glassmorphism p-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-2">areer & Emotional Relief</h3>
        <p>Direct recruiter outreach, higher salary leverage, less job search stress.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">Proof: Real Results from Real Clients</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">📈 “Within 2 weeks, recruiters started reaching out for roles I’d been targeting for months.”</p>
    <p class="mb-4">📈 “I landed 3 interviews in 10 days after my profile was optimized.”</p>
    <p>We’ve optimized <strong>2,500+ profiles</strong> across <strong>25+ industries</strong> with measurable success.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 my-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">Our Indeed Optimization Features</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 text-gray-300">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">🔍 Comprehensive Profile Overhaul</h3>
        <p>100% completion, mobile-friendly formatting, recruiter-first summaries.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">📝 Strategic Content Development</h3>
        <p>Optimized headlines, quantified achievements, skills aligned to Smart Sourcing.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">⚙️ Technical Optimization</h3>
        <p>Indeed Apply compatibility, ATS-proof formatting, recruiter targeting setup.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">📊 Performance Enhancement</h3>
        <p>Profile freshness, screener prep (50% higher chance), analytics tracking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industry Specific -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">Industry-Specific Indeed Optimization</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">💻 Technology & IT</h3>
        <p>Programming skills, certifications, portfolios, and open-source highlights.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">🏥 Healthcare & Medical</h3>
        <p>Licenses, certifications, patient care metrics, specialization keywords.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">📈 Sales & Marketing</h3>
        <p>Revenue achievements, client success stories, digital tool certifications.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">💵 Finance & Banking</h3>
        <p>Portfolio metrics, CPA/CFA certifications, compliance and risk expertise.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 my-10 text-gray-300">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-6">Why Choose Our Indeed Profile Optimization?</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      <li><strong>Certified Specialists:</strong> 2,500+ profiles, 25+ industries, Smart Sourcing expertise.</li>
      <li><strong>Guaranteed Results:</strong> 45% more opportunities or free revision, 48–72 hr delivery.</li>
      <li><strong>Comprehensive Support:</strong> Unlimited revisions, Indeed Apply setup, recruiter analytics.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <section class="bg-white/5 py-10 mt-10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#47C6A2] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li><a href="https://optyp.com/explore/ats-resume/" class="glass-card p-4 block rounded-xl hover:text-[#47C6A2] hover:scale-[1.02] transition">ATS Resume Optimization</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://optyp.com/explore/linkedin/" class="glass-card p-4 block rounded-xl hover:text-[#47C6A2] hover:scale-[1.02] transition">LinkedIn Optimization</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://optyp.com/explore/github/" class="glass-card p-4 block rounded-xl hover:text-[#47C6A2] hover:scale-[1.02] transition">GitHub Optimization</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://optyp.com/explore/portfolio-site/" class="glass-card p-4 block rounded-xl hover:text-[#47C6A2] hover:scale-[1.02] transition">Portfolio-site Optimization</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="text-center py-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Ready to Transform Your Indeed Presence?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Stop being invisible in a sea of 295M resumes. One optimized profile can unlock recruiter calls, 
      premium opportunities, and faster job offers.
    </p>
    <a href="/#contact" 
       class="glass-btn px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 
              border border-[#47C6A2] text-white shadow-md hover:shadow-[#47C6A2]/50 
              hover:bg-[#47C6A2]/20 hover:scale-105">
      Get Your Indeed Optimized Now
    </a>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm">
      ✓ 45% More Opportunities • ✓ 48–72 Hour Delivery • ✓ Certified Indeed Specialists
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
